{"fsPath":"/home/khanh/src/0_github/leetcode/prep/vulcan/01_system_design/SYS-chat-messaging/implementation_blueprint.md","fileUuid":"b02a26a5-ce63-42c4-8cfa-c182741e6a0a","fileSizeBytes":10420,"numLines":345,"diffChanges":[{"originalStartLineNumberOneIndexed":1,"originalEndLineNumberExclusiveOneIndexed":1,"modifiedStartLineNumberOneIndexed":1,"modifiedEndLineNumberExclusiveOneIndexed":346,"addedLines":["# Implementation Blueprint — SYS-chat-messaging (Profile B)","","Muc tieu: xay dung he thong chat chay duoc tren local Linux, can bang giua scale va reliability, co the benchmark de tim tran connection/throughput cua may.","","## 1) Quyet dinh da chot","","### Product scope","","- Loai chat: `1-1 + group` (khong lam channel/room lon trong v1).","- Loai message: rich message khong attachment binary (`text`, `reply`, `edit`, `delete`, `reaction`, `recall`).","- SLA: `1C` — co target cu the theo benchmark:","  - Send->persist ack: p95 <= 120ms, p99 <= 250ms (local benchmark).","  - Persist->delivery (online user): p95 <= 150ms, p99 <= 300ms.","  - Read sync da thiet bi: p95 <= 200ms.","","### Scale model","","- Moi truong: single-node, tach process (`gateway`, `api`, `worker`, `postgres`, `redis`) = Profile B.","- Benchmark muc tieu: ket hop max connection + throughput + tail latency + reconnect.","","### Delivery semantics","","- Chon `effectively exactly-once` (idempotency + dedup) cho message submit va consume.","- ACK strategy: `3C` (tach 3 loai ack):","  - `server_ack`: server da xac nhan request hop le + da persist message.","  - `delivery_ack`: thiet bi online cua recipient da nhan payload.","  - `read_ack`: nguoi dung da doc (cap nhat read pointer).","","### Ordering","","- Trong conversation: `per-conversation sequence number` (monotonic).","- Global ordering: khong can cho product flow, nhung co `global_event_id` cho audit/analytics.","","### Realtime protocol","","- Protocol: WebSocket.","- Ho tro multi-device dong thoi va sync read state.","","### Fanout (muc 6 - quyet dinh)","","- Cross-gateway dispatch: **Redis Streams** (khong dung Pub/Sub thuong).","- Routing strategy: **Hybrid**","  - Presence map trung tam tren Redis: `presence:{user_id}:{device_id} -> gateway_id` (TTL).","  - Gateway co local in-memory session map de push nhanh.","","Ly do chon Redis Streams + Hybrid:","","- Manh hon Pub/Sub cho reliability (co replay, pending, consumer group).","- Don gian hon Kafka/NATS cho local single-node.","- Van du de mo rong khi can test multi-gateway process.","","### Data storage","","- DB chinh: PostgreSQL.","- Message storage: 1 bang `messages` + index `(conversation_id, seq DESC)`.","- Media: chua support binary trong v1.","","### Presence/session","","- Redis set + key TTL.","- Heartbeat 30s, TTL 75s.","- Last seen strong-ish: update disconnect, fallback TTL expiry.","","### Consistency boundary","","- Persist + publish: transactional outbox.","- Bat buoc `client_message_id` cho send API de dedup.","","### API/security","","- Auth: JWT + refresh token.","- Authorization: check membership qua Redis cache + DB fallback + invalidate theo event.","- Abuse control: rate limit user/IP + anti-spam theo conversation.","","### Read model","","- Unread count: tu `last_read_message_id` trong v1.","- Conversation list: query DB + co bo sung cache top conversations theo user.","","### Observability","","- Structured JSON logs + metrics + basic tracing (OpenTelemetry la phase sau).","","### Test/benchmark","","- Unit + integration + reconnect/chaos tests.","- Benchmark tool: k6/artillery truoc, sau do bo sung custom Go loadgen neu can.","","---","","## 2) Kien truc tong the (v1)","","### Components","","- `ws-gateway`: giu WebSocket connection, auth handshake, rate limit, push event.","- `chat-api`: REST cho history/read/state operations.","- `chat-core`: validate, assign sequence, persist message, write outbox.","- `outbox-worker`: doc outbox, publish vao Redis Streams.","- `fanout-worker` (co the nam trong gateway): consume stream, route den gateway co recipient online.","- `presence-service` (logic nam trong gateway + redis helper): heartbeat/session registry.","- `postgres`: source of truth.","- `redis`: presence, membership cache, rate limit counters, streams.","","### Data flow gui tin nhan","","1. Client gui `send_message` qua WebSocket kem `client_message_id`.","2. Gateway xac thuc, authorize membership, goi chat-core.","3. Chat-core transaction:","   - dedup theo `(sender_id, client_message_id)`.","   - cap `seq` theo conversation.","   - insert `messages`.","   - insert `outbox_events`.","4. Tra `server_ack` cho sender sau khi commit.","5. Outbox-worker publish event vao Redis Stream (`chat.conv.{conversation_id}` hoac stream shard).","6. Fanout consumer nhan event, tim device online qua presence map, push den gateway dung.","7. Recipient client gui `delivery_ack`; sender va systems nhan state update.","8. Khi recipient doc, client gui `read_ack`; cap nhat `last_read_message_id`, phat read receipt.","","---","","## 3) Data model blueprint","","### Core tables","","- `users(id, username, created_at, updated_at, ...)`","- `conversations(id, type, name, created_at, updated_at)`","- `members(id, conversation_id, user_id, role, last_read_message_id, joined_at, ...)`","- `messages(id, conversation_id, seq, sender_id, client_message_id, type, body_json, status, created_at, updated_at)`","- `message_receipts(id, message_id, user_id, device_id, receipt_type, receipt_at)` (`delivered` / `read`)","- `outbox_events(id, aggregate_type, aggregate_id, event_type, payload_json, status, created_at, published_at, retry_count)`","- `user_devices(id, user_id, device_id, platform, last_seen_at, ...)`","","### Indexes bat buoc","","- `members(user_id, conversation_id)`","- `members(conversation_id, user_id)` unique","- `messages(conversation_id, seq DESC)`","- `messages(sender_id, client_message_id)` unique (idempotency)","- `message_receipts(message_id, user_id, device_id, receipt_type)` unique","- `outbox_events(status, created_at)`","","### Ordering counter","","Hai cach:","","1. `conversation_sequences(conversation_id PK, last_seq)` + `SELECT ... FOR UPDATE` (de hieu, de benchmark).","2. Sequence allocator theo block (toi uu hon, dung phase sau neu bottleneck).","","Profile B v1 dung cach 1.","","---","","## 4) API / event contract blueprint","","### WebSocket events","","- Client -> Server:","  - `send_message`","  - `ack_delivery`","  - `ack_read`","  - `typing_start` / `typing_stop`","  - `heartbeat`","- Server -> Client:","  - `server_ack`","  - `message_created`","  - `message_updated` (edit/recall/delete/reaction)","  - `delivery_update`","  - `read_update`","  - `presence_update`","  - `error`","","### REST APIs","","- `GET /conversations`","- `POST /conversations` (direct/group)","- `GET /conversations/{id}/messages?cursor&limit`","- `POST /conversations/{id}/read` (cap nhat last_read_message_id)","- `GET /presence/{user_id}` (debug/admin hoac internal)","","### ACK contract (3C)","","- `server_ack`: chua `server_message_id`, `seq`, `accepted_at`.","- `delivery_ack`: chua `message_id`, `device_id`, `delivered_at`.","- `read_ack`: chua `conversation_id`, `last_read_message_id`, `read_at`.","","---","","## 5) Failure handling va trade-offs","","### Reconnect","","- Client reconnect gui `resume_token` + `last_seen_event_id`.","- Gateway replay event chua nhan (dua tren stream + message history cursor).","","### Gateway die","","- Presence key het TTL -> device duoc route sang gateway khac.","- Vi fanout qua Streams + consumer group, event chua ack se duoc claim lai.","","### Duplicate handling","","- Submit duplicate: chan boi unique `(sender_id, client_message_id)`.","- Consume duplicate: `message_receipts` unique key + idempotent update.","","### Trade-off chinh","","- Streams reliable hon Pub/Sub nhung phuc tap hon.","- Outbox tang do tre nhe, doi lai co consistency tot.","- Sequence strong ordering de gap contention tren conversation \"nong\"; can profile.","","---","","## 6) Implementation phases","","### Phase 0 - Scaffold + infra local","","Scope:","","- Monorepo service skeleton (`gateway`, `api`, `worker`, `shared`).","- Docker compose cho Postgres + Redis + observability base.","- Makefile/scripts: run, test, benchmark.","","Done criteria:","","- `docker compose up` chay duoc.","- Healthcheck tat ca service pass.","","### Phase 1 - Core messaging happy path","","Scope:","","- Schema migration core tables.","- Send message qua WS -> persist DB -> `server_ack`.","- Fetch history qua REST.","- Direct/group membership check.","","Done criteria:","","- Integration test: gui 1000 messages, khong mat message.","- Ordering dung theo `seq` trong 1 conversation.","","### Phase 2 - Reliability backbone","","Scope:","","- Transactional outbox.","- Outbox worker publish Redis Streams.","- Fanout worker consume stream, push recipient online.","- Dedup submit (`client_message_id`) + dedup consume.","","Done criteria:","","- Kill/restart worker khong mat event.","- Duplicate send khong tao duplicate message row.","","### Phase 3 - ACK pipeline + read state","","Scope:","","- `delivery_ack`, `read_ack`.","- `message_receipts`.","- Sync read state multi-device.","","Done criteria:","","- Test multi-device: read tren device A cap nhat device B < 300ms p95 local.","","### Phase 4 - Presence + routing","","Scope:","","- Heartbeat, TTL, last_seen.","- Presence map user/device -> gateway.","- Hybrid routing (local session map + redis lookup).","","Done criteria:","","- Reconnect sau gateway restart trong SLA da dat.","- Presence online/offline khong flap qua muc cho phep.","","### Phase 5 - Rich message features","","Scope:","","- reply/edit/delete/reaction/recall.","- Authorization rules cho edit/recall.","- Event versioning cho updates.","","Done criteria:","","- Conflict test (2 updates dong thoi) pass.","- Client state eventually consistent.","","### Phase 6 - Hardening + benchmark","","Scope:","","- Rate limit user/IP + anti-spam conversation.","- Metrics/logging/tracing basic.","- Load test profiles: connection ceiling, throughput, mixed workload.","- Kernel/app tuning guide cho Linux local.","","Done criteria:","","- Co bao cao benchmark (p50/p95/p99, msg/s, max conn, error rate).","- Co danh sach bottleneck top-5 va action tiep theo.","","---","","## 7) Benchmark blueprint (Profile B local)","","### Workload profiles","","- `W1 Connection ceiling`: mo dan WS toi khi error rate > 1%.","- `W2 Throughput`: giu connection co dinh, tang send rate.","- `W3 Mixed`: 70% receive, 20% send, 10% read/presence/reconnect.","- `W4 Failure`: restart worker/gateway trong luc co traffic.","","### KPI can thu","","- Max concurrent WS connections.","- Msg/s accepted va delivered.","- p50/p95/p99:","  - send->server_ack","  - send->recipient_delivery","  - read->read_sync","- CPU/RAM/FD usage theo service.","- Duplicate rate, dropped connection rate, reconnect success rate.","","### Linux tuning checklist (thuc hien truoc benchmark lon)","","- Tang `ulimit -n`.","- Tune `somaxconn`, `tcp_max_syn_backlog`, `ip_local_port_range`.","- Theo doi GC/memory profile service.","","---","","## 8) Definition of done (toan project v1)","","- Chay duoc end-to-end tren local bang 1 lenh bootstrap.","- Pass unit + integration + reconnect tests.","- Co benchmark report lap lai duoc.","- Co tai lieu kien truc, schema, protocol event, runbook su co co ban.","- Co danh sach backlog v2 (attachment binary, OpenTelemetry full, sharding xa hon).",""],"tokenizedAddedLines":[1000000,1000001,1000002,1000001,1000003,1000001,1000004,1000001,1000005,1000006,1000007,1000008,1000009,1000010,1000001,1000011,1000001,1000012,1000013,1000001,1000014,1000001,1000015,1000016,1000017,1000018,1000019,1000001,1000020,1000001,1000021,1000022,1000001,1000023,1000001,1000024,1000025,1000001,1000026,1000001,1000027,1000028,1000029,1000030,1000001,1000031,1000001,1000032,1000033,1000034,1000001,1000035,1000001,1000036,1000037,1000038,1000001,